            I grew to merge creativity with practicality, crafting designs that
            resonate with users.
          </p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article
          class="mt-6 flex w-full gap-2"
        >
        <div class="w-1 bg-accent"></div>
        <div class="flex w-full flex-col items-start py-1 px-2 max-md:max-w-full max-md:pl-5">
          <h3
            class="text-sm font-semibold leading-none tracking-tighter text-white"
